Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:38.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo pre ľudí, čo sa nesmie vyčerpať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:47.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je tiež dôležité, ale hovorím o "snoch."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš zjesť sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:54.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bez snov život nemá zmysel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:04.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie je ľahké pre ľudí udržať sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:09.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď je "osoba" pridaná do "sna"... Dokážeš to prečítať?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedokážem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Číta sa to "ľahké."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:22.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj život je ľahký...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:25.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako aj Siriusov...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:35.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri sa na ruku...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:38.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa snažíš pochopiť sny, tak ti prekĺznu pomedzi prsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:41.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko záleží na tej ruke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:59.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:16.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Pod vysvieteným kopcom sme si vyznali počiatok lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Kvôli tebe a aj sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:30.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po tisícročiach osamelosti som sa stretla s tvojim uhrančivým pohľadom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:36.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem byť spojená!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:41.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to príjemný pocit vzrušenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:47.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to, ako keby sa táto sila zrodila z morskej peny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Tieto slzy dojatia, to rozhodne nie je žiaden sen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}toto je útek za láskou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Všetko čo máme sú naše srdcia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Naše nádeje sú v nekonečnej čiernej diere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:10.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem, aby sme boli spojení, a to naveky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:27.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(442,368)}"Ľahké krídla"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia a všetci... Pozerajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:29.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite čo ľudia spravili Anjelom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:32.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo ste vy spravili svojim vlastným priateľom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol si statočný, ako dobrovoľník.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudskosť dokáže poraziť Ťieňových Anjelov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šlo to perfektne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Transplantovanie peria Ťieňových Anjelov na teba
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,zvýši tvoje schopnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:27.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, zdá sa, že sa stal veľmi citlivým.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne Ťieňoví Anjely majú systém vedomia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ktorý je tak odlišný od ľudského.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zlyhali sme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:38.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, musíme len nainštalovať zábranu citlivosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ničoho sa nemusíš báť, Glen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš v poriadku. Nechaj to na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš, že to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale mal pierka Ťieňových Anjelov!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni by nemali...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Transplantovali... pierka toho dieťaťa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké kruté!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kruté?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:06.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierka Ťieňových Anjelov zvýšia fyzické schopnosti ľudí na hranicu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:12.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto musí byť Útočný Aquarion riadený jednotlivcom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediný šíp, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:34.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, odpusť mi! A Glen, prosím nebojuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav toto šialenstvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten útok bol úžasný! Obyčajný človek by to nedokázal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže tiež chceš pierka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to som...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:02.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sklamal si ma, Glen... bojovať s takou hnusnou zbraňou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozdelil sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednotenie zabralo 2.2 sekundy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je neľudsky rýchle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Už nie je človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musíš bojovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musíte obaja... Prečo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:21.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Boli sme priatelia! Dobrý priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:18.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierka Futaba boli použité... ako zlé sily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:26.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko, čo to dieťa vedelo, bolo sa len dobre zasmiať...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neuveriteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:06.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sme mali ešte 10 takých, ľudstvo by vyhralo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediný šíp sa ľahko zlomí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme vyhrať, je jedno koľko ich máme,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,kým je ľudstvo hlúpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám tu Cherubína Marsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:29.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia... Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:35.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz chápeš? Aký odporný vedia ľudia byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby vyhrali, tak si vždy odpustia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:44.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Deava a tí s perím, ako ty a ja,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,nie sú nič viac, než morské prasiatka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď, Silvie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď ku mne...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem... to spraviť!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ku komu hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde som?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia sa teleportovala do Útočného Vectora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Alfa! Glen, si tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:26.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedovoľ, aby šla Silvia za ním! Zostrel ju, ak to bude nutné!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:37.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš, že Sirius príde k sebe, len preto, že ho volá jeho sestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:43.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, príde. Majú rovnakú krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:50.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dvaja sú jeden. A jeden sú obaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeden sa rozdelil do dvoch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:56.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz sa snaží spojiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:59.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to vyššia sila.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:03.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poškodenie pohonného systému Útočného Vectora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je zameraný na jeho stav bez Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepoužiteľný bezpilotný Vector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pilot nezranený!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:18.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť! Ako mohol byť Útočný typ tak ľahko porazený?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:22.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poviem ti. Jeden šíp sa ľahko zlomí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak čo môžeme spraviť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehľadaj odpoveď u ostatných!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:32.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je vždy v tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:50.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3. aura citov elementu Sol rýchlo narastá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Energický kryštál Vectoru Sol rezonuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sám sa opravuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechoď!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenechám ťa ísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednotím sa s tebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Núdzový Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za silu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo do-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som hlava!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je šialený! Vynútené zjednotenie s vojenským Vectorom Omega!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekliaty bezkrídli! Ako ste sa opovážili zobrať mi Silviu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte raz! Zjednotenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:05.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherubín Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sám sa opravuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Další vojak Cherubín!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvaj ma, Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:18.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš bojovať proti mne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš bojovať proti mne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:21.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:26.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak sa pridaj na moju stranu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechoď, Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius! Prečo trápiš Silviu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť sa k nám!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:48.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Klesneš na úroveň hnusných ľudí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaja majú krídla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako Ťieňoví Anjely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia bola Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius-sempai, tiež...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:22.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť! Nikto mi nepovedal, že boli Ťieňoví Anjely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:27.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak čo si povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Boli transplantované, ako u Glena?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Náramky! Obaja mali stále náramky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:39.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že sa tak narodili?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:44.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak narodením začína ľudský život, tak nepotrebujeme sny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Plnením snov, môžu ľudia prekonať ich narodenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:53.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To robí človeka človekom! To robia sny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:16:00.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty a ja máme iba mäso a krv na tomto svete...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,S tvojimi a mojim krídlami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spolu, môžeme dokázať hocičo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:10.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, aj lietať...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:16.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej Silvia! Princezná chromá! Počuješ ma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď, Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:27.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chyť ma za ruku a leťme... vysoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:43.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripojíš sa v lietaní v oblakoch a budeš sa pozerať na ľudí na zemi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:48.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si rovnaká, ako Sirius? Si až taká úbohá?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:52.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrime, kto hovorí o "úbohosti."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo dokážeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si bezkrídly, ktorý nedokáže dokonca ani lietať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno neviem lietať. Možno ani nebudem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale dokážem uchopiť môj sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:24.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Netušil som, že si až taký veľký hlupák, Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:28.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ Fudo ťa dobre vycvičil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Beštia ako ty... drží svoj sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:35.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké smiešne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak poď, Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:01.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už chápem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto pravá ruka bez krídla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:12.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je tu preto, aby sa s tebou spojila, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:17.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu preto, aby sa spojila, s niekým koho milujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:27.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je ti jedno, že nebudeš lietať?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, aj keď to znamená plazenie po zemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumieš tejto bolesti?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolesti, že ťa nechápe vlastná sestra,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ktorú som ľúbil viac, než hocikoho iného?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:51.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo mi spôsobuje bolesť... musí byť oddelené!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Reika! Dajte mi ruku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne si si istá?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nie je o boji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:09.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je môj brat a už tomu rozumiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to spravíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Traja ako jeden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Osamelý meč anjela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,183)}"Osamelý meč anjela"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:23.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príliš jednoduché!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zablokoval to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, teraz mám šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:11.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia, to bolo veľmi dobré...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:27.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, všetkým...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Mars sa vrátil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:38.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátiť sa kapitán Glen a Útočné Vectory Alfa a Delta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:43.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A zavolajte späť Reiku, Apolla a Silviu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Automatický systém...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:09.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pierko z dieťaťa Ťieňového Anjela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:24.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudia vždy spravia to, čo považujú v daný čas za najlepšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:29.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale často sa to zmení, na hlúpe rozhodnutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:33.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je smutné na tom, byť človek...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:44.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Má sa vaša milovaná dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:50.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Do vtedy, kým sa ku mne nevráti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:55.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:22:00.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty a ja môžeme konečne stáť na jednej strane...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:47.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiki-Sempai, mám prosbu pred ďalšou rozhodujúcou bitkou...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Akú, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:51.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dáte mi váš gombík?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:54.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Č-Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:55.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Nebeská brána"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:58.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(459,404)}"Nebeská brána"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:58.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, na čo to potrebuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
